data.text:
2023-2024 - Points

Zach LaVine scores a season high 51 points for Chicago Bulls

On October 10, 2023, Zach LaVine set a season high in points in a NBA game. That day he scored 51 points in Chicago Bulls's road loss against Detroit Pistons, 118-102. He also had 4 rebounds, 1 steal and finished the game with a 38 efficiency.

2023-2024 - Rebounds

Andre Drummond grabs a season high 26 rebounds for Chicago Bulls

On February 02, 2024, Andre Drummond set a season high in rebounds in a NBA game. That day he grabbed 26 rebounds in Chicago Bulls's home win against Cleveland Cavaliers, 132-123. He also had 17 points, 1 assist and finished the game with a 39 efficiency.

2023-2024 - Assists

Jevon Carter dishes a season high 12 assists for Chicago Bulls

On April 04, 2024, Jevon Carter set a season high in assists in a NBA game. That day he dished 12 assists in Chicago Bulls's road win against Washington Wizards, 127-129. He also had 20 points, 2 rebounds, 1 steal and finished the game with a 28 efficiency.

2023-2024 - Steals

Alex Caruso has a season high 5 steals for Chicago Bulls

On February 02, 2024, Alex Caruso set a season high in steals in a NBA game. That day he reached 5 steals in Chicago Bulls's home loss against Detroit Pistons, 95-105. He also had 4 points, 2 rebounds, 5 steals and finished the game with a 4 efficiency.

2023-2024 - Blocks

Alex Caruso blocks a season high 4 blocks for Chicago Bulls Alex Caruso

On February 02, 2024, Alex Caruso set a season high in blocks in a NBA game. That day he went for 4 blocks in Chicago Bulls's home win against Minnesota Timberwolves, 129-123. He also had 3 points, 9 rebounds, 2 steals and finished the game with a 16 efficiency.

2023-2024 - Efficiency

Coby White set a season high 52 efficiency for Chicago Bulls

On April 04, 2024, Coby White set a season high in efficiency in a NBA Play-In Tournament game. That day he accomplished 52 efficiency in Chicago Bulls's home win against Atlanta Hawks, 131-116. He also had 42 points, 9 rebounds, 2 steals and finished the game with a 52 efficiency.
